text:
This one is definetly more disco-ish than the one from Colosseum. I don't know which I like better.
I love a ton of the music from this game. The theme of the SS Libra, the ONBS building, and the boss and Shadow Lugia themes were definitely my favorite tracks.
But although it has a lot of nice music, I noticed that they're all much shorter, so they can get a bit repetitive. It's definitely not Plok.
Also, Colosseum was a lot... darker... than this game, which makes it cooler imo.
